description: Starts the IdMappingJob of a workflow. The workflow must have previously been created using the CreateIdMappingWorkflow endpoint.

parameters.name: workflowName
parameters.description: The name of the ID mapping job to be retrieved.

parameters.name: outputSourceConfig
parameters.description: A list of OutputSource objects. (dict) --- An object containing KMSArn, OutputS3Path, and RoleARN. The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM role. Entity Resolution assumes this role to access Amazon Web Services resources on your behalf as part of workflow execution. The S3 path to which Entity Resolution will write the output table. KMSArn (string) --- Customer KMS ARN for encryption at rest. If not provided, system will use an Entity Resolution managed KMS key.

nested_params.name: outputS3Path

nested_params.description: Customer KMS ARN for encryption at rest. If not provided, system will use an Entity Resolution managed KMS key.
